blog.name: the-pansexual-labyrinthian
blog.title: Some Pun about being Pan and loving D&D
blog.description: What up bitches, I'm here, I'm Pan, and I love D&D. I'm a huge fan of Critical Role, High Rollers, and Dice Camera Action (all though I'm far behind). I'll be posting some of my own stuff sometimes too :3

tags: please be kind to me because of my limited knowledge
body:
Okay so

I’ve only seen about 10 minutes of Campaign one, so my knowledge is very limited. What I do know is these things:

Vax: Lucky Bastard

Vex: Penny Pincher that marries Percy

Percy: Irredeemable bastard man that get redemption. Formerly No Mercy Percy.

Grog: Owns a bag of holding I think? Hits stuff really hard. The best at drawing from the DoMT.

Pike: Paladin I believe? Not sure though.

Scanlan: Halts just short (haha pun). Is the residential Bard, and is the hugest stereotypical bard. Again not sure.

Keyleth: Laura Bailey but as a Druid with antlers.

Trinket: A literal fucking bear. That gives great massages.

I also know they die a lot, and I think Vex dies first. And uhhhhmmm….There’s a Totem of the Duck Barbarian that likes chocolate milk. Oh and the group is Vox Machina.

Edit: I have been informed that Pike is a Cleric, and that Keyleth is like Vex but the opposite.
